Generated the I Scroll Bar developer guide at `generated/i-scroll-bar.md`. The document covers:

- Creating a ScrollBar using `ScrollBar::New()`
- Configuring scroll bar visibility with `ScrollBarVisibility` enum (Auto, Always, Never)
- Updating scroll bar state with `UpdateBarSize()`, `UpdateScrollPosition()`, and `HideBar()`
- Styling options including thickness, color, minimum size, offset, and corner radius

All API usages and default values were verified against the public headers (`i-scroll-bar.h`, `scroll-bar.h`, `scrollable-enum.h`) and UTC test file (`utc-Dali-ScrollBar.cpp`).
